dataIdInfo.idAbs:
These boundaries are being rolled out in stages from 21 September 2015. The last region to transition to the new boundaries will do so on 29 February 2016, at which point this dataset will represent the current DOC structure.

These boundaries replace the existing Services District boundaries which were in place from 2 September 2013.

The following District Boundaries were realigned on 01/07/2019 (database edits on 18/06/2019): Coastal Otago, Geraldine
